Troubleshooting Tips
Issue: Cannot connect to PostgreSQL

Check service status: sudo systemctl status postgresql
Verify credentials in db_config.sh
Check pg_hba.conf for authentication settings
Issue: Permission denied on scripts

Make scripts executable: chmod +x *.sh
Check file ownership: ls -l
Issue: Migration fails with syntax error

Review SQL syntax in migration file
Test SQL directly in psql first
Check for missing semicolons or quotes
Issue: Backup file not created

Verify backup directory exists
Check disk space: df -h
Review pg_dump permissions
